3265.Name: 2022 "A" & "B" Districts
3265.Details:
"A" & "B" Districts will be held on Saturday March 26 at various clubs. All finals will be back at Shadow Lake. Entry fee includes 3 matches, pizza/beer & favor. 
Cost is $42/person
"A" means levels 1-3
"B" means levels 4+
16 max teams per draw, no exceptions so sign up early!
3265.RegistrationDetails: Please register your team. One person only per team needs to register. I will collect money in March for this event with cash or venmo. Please put your Session 3 level.
